", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已在倫蒂尼姆見到太多無意義的屠戮。失去理智的薩卡茲理應由同胞之手阻止。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g4_ordnancefactory", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好意思，博士......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我還以為我只是陪你回家。;我們是不是很不受歡迎？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line121", "option2": "line121"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......去年我從廠裡逃出去的時候，和奶奶吵了一架。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_660_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十來個身強力壯的工人把你們團團圍住。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們每一個的眼神裡都充滿了警惕。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看了看他們手裡的鑽頭和扳手，又看了看與他們裝扮近似，卻形單影隻的費斯特。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "感覺不像吵了一架那麼簡單。;你確定我們不是被當成敵人了？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line143", "option2": "line143"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來奶奶還是很生氣......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有必要對一個死人生氣。畢竟直到剛剛，我都不知道自己唯一的孫子還活著。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想過給廠裡發消息，但是這太冒險了，薩卡茲會監控海布里區收到的每一條訊息。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能讓薩卡茲知道你們和自救軍有聯繫。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼說，你加入了那個什麼荒唐團隊。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......倫蒂尼姆市民自救軍。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#11$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶，我們在薩迪恩區做了很多事，薩卡茲控制了報社和電視台，他們故意把我們稱作不知名的暴力集團......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼說，確實是你們炸了城牆。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#6$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......是博......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "是薩卡茲對自救軍的追捕導致了倫蒂尼姆城牆的損失。;您的孫子在那一戰中表現得十分英勇。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line164", "option2": "line167"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line171"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......對，主要是薩卡茲幹的。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line171"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，博士。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是負責為你綁了幾根滑索，沒想到你對我評價這麼高。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你這趟回來，是想把我們的軍工廠也炸了嗎？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......怎麼可能？！", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是怎麼對你的自救軍朋友說的？我們這些廠正在為薩卡茲生產武器，而這些武器最終都會指向維多利亞人？", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#8$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，奶奶，我告訴他們的是——", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的奶奶為了保護其他人的生活，而選擇站了出來。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#5$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶，我知道我在你眼裡只是一個愛耍小聰明的小鬼。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我不是為了把廠裡的大夥捲進來而回來的，我也不是為了說服你而回來的。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我確實有我的目的，能讓你幫助我自然是再好不過，但是首先——", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想看到，你平安無事。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過來，讓我看看。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奶奶......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "臭小子，長高了啊。", "name": "凱瑟琳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_648_1#10$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_648_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，長高了一點。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就快得到那樣東西了。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒸汽騎士的甲胄——這玩意兒有多少人搶著要？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊塔尼亞的貴族們最喜歡用類似的古董裝點門面。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，也問問哥倫比亞的那幾家公司，就算是幾百年前的技術，他們說不定也感興趣。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "運出去不是問題，你以為我在眼下的倫蒂尼姆靠什麼做生意？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那幫薩卡茲是講不通道理的瘋子，但光憑他們可統治不了倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在城防軍有很可靠的朋友，他們能幫我搞定的。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯一的問題是——聽說我盯上的那具品相可不是很好，希望別折價。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼擔心折價的話，不如放棄吧。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰在那裡？！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別怕，我們只是碰巧同路而已。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快把這個人給我弄走！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，我請的保鏢......保鏢呢？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我請他們在路口休息一會，等我們聊完天，你就能去找他們。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你把他們都......你只有一個人！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個人？抱歉，從來不止。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#8$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "注意你的身後。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們......這是倫蒂尼姆！我的朋友你們可惹不起——", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_unsheathe", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位朋友在哪呢？搞不好和我挺投緣？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咿！！別衝動！！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可從來不會一上來就動拳頭，只要你老實點就行。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王說什麼，你就聽什麼。懂了嗎？", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不然，我的鋼爪下一次落下的時候，瞄準的就不會是這堵牆了。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_iron_claw", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知、知道了！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒搞錯吧？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#5$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最起勁的居然是你。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#9$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們教我的。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#8$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，放開他吧。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚嗚......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "珀蒂先生。請睜開眼，也不必費勁舉著雙手了。我們不會傷害你......至少現在不會。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們到底要什麼？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的條件已經說清楚了。請你放棄覬覦坎伯蘭家的蒸汽騎士甲胄。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我答應了你就會放我走嗎？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我會確保你履行我們之間的約定。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根，把我們的地圖給珀蒂先生看一眼。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_scroll", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地圖？這些標注出來的地方都是我的臨時倉庫......你們怎麼會知道？！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以後出門的時候，你最好再多注意一下四周。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們找人跟蹤了我？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說得沒錯，薩卡茲可不會被收買，一旦他們知道你借用的那點“關係”讓你偷偷地把這麼多違禁物品運進倫蒂尼姆......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時候，你猜你的那位朋友會不會救你？你猜他自己會是什麼下場？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在考慮主動找薩卡茲報信。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真要這麼做的話，我們或許誰都逃不了。可你要是繼續與我們合作的話，薩卡茲什麼都不會知道。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我還能選什麼呢？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我理解你的不易，也珍惜與你交易的機會。該給的酬勞，我們一分都不會少。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......等等。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，你和阿勒黛·坎伯蘭是什麼關係？你是她的扈從嗎？不，坎伯蘭家早就空了，哪裡還請得起扈從？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "胡說八道，那個坎伯蘭是維娜的扈從還差不多！", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#7$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她可是大公爵的女兒！難道說......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你搞錯了，我誰都不是。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_177", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "非要說的話，我和坎伯蘭小姐是同伴，我們身後還有千千萬萬同樣渴望和平的倫蒂尼姆人。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "珀蒂先生，但願你也不例外。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_407_1#3$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g3_school_indoor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "block": "true", "image": "blocker_movi", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "第四幕\\n——————\\n第三場", "x": 300.0, "y": 320.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 27.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spotlight", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_spotlight", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有忠誠於這片土地的戰士都在我的身後。與邪惡的決戰就在眼前......", "name": "騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們......是居住在這裡的孩子嗎？", "name": "騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別躲在街角的陰影裡，或許你們還無法舉起什麼武器......", "name": "騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但從不是只有手握武器的人才是戰士。你們必須得睜開眼睛，去看，去聽，去判斷。", "name": "騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們已經足以告訴我什麼是對的，什麼是錯的，什麼是你們想要的生活。", "name": "騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，我將前進。而你們，則見證。", "name": "騎士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spotlight", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太棒啦！戈爾丁女士，您看拉爾夫演得多好......這孩子可真是長大啦，四年前他還像個調皮搗蛋的小獸！", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，我也很高興。茉莉，你需要手帕嗎？", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "手帕？對對，我可不能讓眼淚弄髒衣裳，在孩子們面前太不體面了......真是忍不住啊，一想到拉爾夫他們很快就要離開學校，我就......", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子們該休息一會了，我們也多了一點喘氣的時間。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對啊，還有最後一幕......最後一幕才是最精彩的。", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#1$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_strangeclap", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰在鼓掌？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天只是試演，您沒邀請什麼街坊朋友過來看吧？", "name": "茉莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_657_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#10$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師們的視線投向教室的最後一排。"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個穿著軍裝的男人坐在距離門口最近的角落裡，緩慢而堅定地鼓著掌。"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是精彩的演出。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......萊托中校。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到城防軍指揮官大人會有空蒞臨我們這間小小的教室。", "name": "戈爾丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_647_1#4$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "午安，女士們。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}